      <entry xml:id="entry_tæraz" xml:lang="os" abv:completeness="incomplete">
        <form xml:id="form_d95e66" type="lemma" xml:lang="os-x-iron"><orth>tæraz</orth></form>
        <form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>tæræzæ</orth></form>
        <sense xml:id="sense_d95e69">
          <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
            <q>весы</q>
          </abv:tr>
        </sense>
        <re>
          <note type="comment">син. </note>
          <form type="lemma"><orth>baræn; tæræztæ</orth></form>
          <sense>
            <tr xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict" xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">весы двухчашечные</q>
            </tr>
          </sense>
        </re>
        <exampleGrp xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict">
          <example>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">wælæ arvyl tæræztæ, æz syl mæxī
              barӡynæn</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">вот на небе весы, я на них взвешусь</q>
            </tr>
            <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_ОТ"/>
              <biblScope>42</biblScope></bibl>
          </example>
          <example>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">tærazæj barægaw</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">как бы взвешивая на весах</q>
            </tr>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">тщательно взвешивая</q>
            </tr>
          </example>
        </exampleGrp>
        <etym xml:lang="ru">Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
            <w>tarāzū</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="pal"><lang/>
            <w>tarāzūk</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="tg"><lang/>
            <w>tarozu</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ku" extralang="ps"><lang/>
            <w>tarāzū</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sgh"><lang/>
            <w>tirozi</w>
            <gloss><q>весы</q></gloss></mentioned>. Вошло во многие языки: <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><lang/>
            <w>tārazə</w>, <w>tæræzi</w></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Радлов"/>
            <biblScope>III 1060, 1064</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/>
            <w>tarazo</w>
            <gloss><q>уровень</q> (инструмент), <q>ватерпас</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref
              type="bibl" target="#ref_Груз._сл."/>
            <biblScope>IV 339</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned xml:lang="lez"><lang/>
            <w>terez</w>, <w>terezar</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ce"><lang/>
            <w>terza</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><lang/>
            <w>taraz</w>
            <gloss><q>весы</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Мациев"/>
            <biblScope>399</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><title>Чеч.-инг.-русск. сл.</title>
            <pubPlace>Грозный</pubPlace>, <date>1962</date>, <biblScope>стр.
          143</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><lang/>
            <w>täräzä</w>
            <gloss><q>весы</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ady"><lang/>
            <w>täräz</w>
            <gloss><q>правильно</q>, <q>точно</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl"
              target="#ref_Хатанов_Керашева"/>
            <biblScope>556</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned xml:lang="uby"><lang/>
            <w>ɣe-terezə</w>
            <gloss><q>делать точным</q>, <q>rendre exact</q></gloss></mentioned>
              (<bibl><author>Dumézil</author>. <title>Récits oubykh</title>. <date>JA 1955</date>,
              <biblScope>стр. 46</biblScope></bibl>); далее <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/>
            (донской говор) <w>тереза́</w>
            <gloss><q>большие весы</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="orv"><lang/>
            <w>тереза</w>
            <gloss><q>весы</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="uk"><lang/>
            <w>терези́</w> (мн. ч.)</mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sh"><lang/>
            <w>teresije</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ro"><lang/>
            <w>terezie</w>
            <gloss>id.</gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Lokotsch"/>
            <biblScope>159</biblScope></bibl>). <emph>Hübschmann</emph> со ссылкой на
            <emph>Ahlqvist</emph> (<bibl><title>Gramm.</title>
            <biblScope>176</biblScope></bibl>) производит также <mentioned xml:lang="x-mordvin"
            ><lang/> (мокша) <w>teraza</w></mentioned>. — В осетинский могло войти из тюркских
          языков. <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Hübschmann._Oss."/>
            <biblScope>132</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
      </entry>
